  "2271930": {
    "name": "落日余晖",
    "steam_appid": 2271930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/c8b061de18cd88faa48f66d9e273a225.poster.avif?t=1759306400\" width=1170 height=617 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/c8b061de18cd88faa48f66d9e273a225.webm?t=1759306400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >落日余晖是一款在神秘岛屿鲁米诺拉展开的开放世界生存游戏，这里沉睡着海盗的宝藏和海妖的传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在白天，你可以探索这片广袤的土地，收集资源、狩猎野兽、耕种农田、垂钓捕鱼，打造你的武器与防具。建立属于你的要塞。与遍布岛上的怪物战斗，磨练你的战斗技巧，挑战沉睡在远古时光中的首领怪物，揭开岛屿的重重谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当当夜幕降临，这座岛屿将坠入黑暗，化作死亡之地。武装好自己，在亡灵的围攻中存活到黎明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好了吗？扬帆起航，征服这片未知的岛屿！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在白天探索这片神秘之地！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/f5b05fef050a5f6b4a534e0411653598.poster.avif?t=1759306400\" width=1170 height=617 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/f5b05fef050a5f6b4a534e0411653598.webm?t=1759306400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将以一名落难者的身份来到这座岛屿，身无长物，只剩一件破旧的衣衫。从海岸线出发，穿越茂密的丛林，跋涉广袤的沙漠，探索这个庞大的开放世界。你需要探索这座诅咒之岛，收集生存物资，寻找神秘的「克图格亚之石」。当你深入岛屿腹地，更多令人震惊的秘密等待着你去发现。揭开这个世界隐藏的远古谜团吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制定你的生存战略，在恐怖的黑夜中求生！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/104dddd3575e86287cf29be55d653025.poster.avif?t=1759306400\" width=1170 height=617 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/104dddd3575e86287cf29be55d653025.webm?t=1759306400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每当夜幕降临，无数亡灵将蜂拥而至。无论你藏身何处，它们都会执着地追寻你的踪迹。建造坚固的要塞来应对黑夜，设置巧妙的陷阱和障碍来阻挡亡灵。记住，有备无患，这是在这片土地上生存的关键！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验紧张刺激的战斗！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/9738a681ff4bd93d858778ab024b15e3.poster.avif?t=1759306400\" width=1170 height=617 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/9738a681ff4bd93d858778ab024b15e3.webm?t=1759306400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上远古的亡灵虎视眈眈，伺机而动。提升你的能力，磨练战斗技巧，在这场激烈的动作冒险中与无数敌人展开殊死搏斗！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与伙伴一同冒险！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/9cd0c87e0d834a54cd31f43ddcd4bd36.poster.avif?t=1759306400\" width=1170 height=617 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271930/extras/9cd0c87e0d834a54cd31f43ddcd4bd36.webm?t=1759306400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以与其他幸存者并肩作战，共同劳作，分享资源，谋划生存之道。与值得信赖的伙伴一同冒险，将让你的旅程更加精彩！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 韩语, 日语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 土耳其语, 印地语, 阿拉伯语",
